{"tid":1690661,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"太古城施襲恐怖份子操普通話","createTime":"2019-11-03T11:53:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T12:07:56.000Z","uid":5195,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8b4e6b0145153d65d6f7e4002bf185593bf470cf","tid":1690661,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T11:53:16.000Z","msg":"【1937 太古城】現場消息指，有操普通話男子持刀襲擊市民。有市民耳部受傷浴血，至少3人受傷。疑是施襲者的灰衫男則被打至血流披面，及後他站起拿著一個垃圾筒奸笑，隨即掟走逃跑，但被市民阻截。混亂間有人被該男子捉住當人質，最後被其他市民救走。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果即時"},{"pid":"bb168267319882caacc0d2fe8016c1d17151409f","tid":1690661,"uid":318062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T11:54:30.000Z","msg":"【重要】解決和理非走得快過勇武嘅方法 全民哨兵<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1690586\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1690586</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8c53d99622d233a4368e8d47f05bafd3c00b3344","tid":1690661,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T11:55:02.000Z","msg":"大陸人"},{"pid":"7f78350f95a6459b836ce0814cb3e786f8760cbb","tid":1690661,"uid":207087,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T12:00:46.000Z","msg":"每日150的共業<br />\n已經落咗超過五十萬，只要其中百分之一係冇人性暴徒，港豬分分鐘會被劏"},{"pid":"89161f89ad52781bc7d8af63166c3a8cb9ccc687","tid":1690661,"uid":28970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T12:02:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EJwW9Qo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEJwW9Qo.jpg&h=ee2534c5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jDxzb3J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjDxzb3J.jpg&h=32581155&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2da4534de007dfb350fbcec19b362c6497eda3fb","tid":1690661,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T12:03:24.000Z","msg":"填命"},{"pid":"13cef71dbbdb1f6653737087b8388b9f9557caa1","tid":1690661,"uid":254594,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T